  pango.glyph.lisp - Storing information about glyphs             - Pango 1.51 &
  pango.attributes.lisp - Attributes for annotating text          - Pango 1.54
  pango.markup.lisp - Markup language for text with attributes    - Pango 1.51 &
  pango.layout.lisp - High-level layout driver objects            - Pango 1.51
  pango.script.lisp - Scripts and Languages                       - Pango 1.51 &
  pango.bidirectional.lisp - Handling bidirectional text          - Pango 1.51
  pango.gravity.lisp - Text layout in vertical directions         - Pango 1.51

